WEBVTT

00:04:59.320 --> 00:05:02.216
in order to speak about the climate.

00:05:02.240 --> 00:05:03.976
(Laughter)

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:05.256
For 14 minutes.

00:05:05.280 --> 00:05:09.176
(Laughter)

00:05:09.200 --> 00:05:11.896
So that makes me
want to move on to denial.

00:05:11.920 --> 00:05:14.176
(Laughter)

00:05:14.200 --> 00:05:15.976
So if we keep silent,

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:20.056
ignore or ridicule facts
about climate disruptions,

00:05:20.080 --> 00:05:22.896
then we might find inner refuge

00:05:22.920 --> 00:05:24.360
from fear and guilt.

00:05:25.200 --> 00:05:28.896
Denial doesn't really come
from lack of intelligence or knowledge.

00:05:28.920 --> 00:05:32.216
No, denial is a state of mind